3) Commission > 25% of salary

**Aim: To find employees with high commission.** \
Requirement: Salary and commission fields.\
Theory: Arithmetic comparison filters records.\
Query: SELECT ename, sal, comm
FROM employee
WHERE comm > 0.25 * sal;
