7) Last Sunday of current month

**Aim: To find last Sunday.** \
Requirement: Date functions.\
Theory: LAST_DAY and weekday adjustment.\
Query: SELECT DATE_SUB(LAST_DAY(CURDATE()),
INTERVAL (DAYOFWEEK(LAST_DAY(CURDATE()))-1) DAY);
